<div class="mb-6">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Help Center</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Learn how to use ParroByte CRM effectively</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
    <!-- Getting Started -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 p-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><i class="ri-rocket-line text-pink-500"></i> Getting Started</h3>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full btn-pink text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Create a WhatsApp Session</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Go to <strong>WhatsApp Sessions</strong> and click "New Session". Give it a name and scan the QR code with your phone's WhatsApp app.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full btn-pink text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Add Contacts</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Navigate to <strong>Contacts</strong> and add contacts manually or upload a CSV file with your contact list.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full btn-pink text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Send Messages</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Go to <strong>Messages</strong>, select your session, choose contacts, and send your message.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Sessions FAQ -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 p-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><i class="ri-qr-code-line text-pink-500"></i> WhatsApp Sessions</h3>
      <div class="join join-vertical w-full">
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="sessions-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">How do I connect a WhatsApp session?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>Click "New Session", give it a name, then scan the displayed QR code using WhatsApp on your phone (Settings > Linked Devices > Link a Device).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="sessions-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Why did my session disconnect?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>Sessions may disconnect if your phone loses internet, WhatsApp is closed on your phone, or the session expires. Click "Reconnect" to restore.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="sessions-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">How many sessions can I have?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>Free: 1, Silver: 3, Gold: 10, Platinum: Unlimited sessions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Messages FAQ -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 p-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><i class="ri-message-3-line text-pink-500"></i> Messaging</h3>
      <div class="join join-vertical w-full">
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="messages-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">What is the rate limit?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>To prevent account bans, we limit to 30 messages per minute per account. This helps keep your WhatsApp account safe.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="messages-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Can I send media files?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>Yes! You can send images, documents, and videos. Use templates to save media for reuse.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="messages-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">How do I schedule messages?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>Go to <strong>Schedule</strong>, select contacts, write your message, and pick a date/time. The system will send it automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Auto Reply FAQ -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 p-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><i class="ri-robot-line text-pink-500"></i> Auto Reply</h3>
      <div class="join join-vertical w-full">
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="autoreply-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">How does auto reply work?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>Set up rules that match incoming messages and automatically send responses. Supports exact match, contains, starts/ends with, and regex.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mb-2">
          <input type="radio" name="autoreply-faq" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">What is AI response?</div>
          <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p>AI response lets you define a prompt template. When a message matches, the system uses your prompt to generate a contextual reply.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2"><i class="ri-customer-service-line"></i> Still Need Help?</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-pink-100 mb-4">Our support team is ready to assist you.</p>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-pink-100">
          <i class="ri-mail-line"></i> support@whatsappcrm.com
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 p-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Quick Links</h3>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-pink-50 transition-colors text-sm text-gray-700">
          <i class="ri-dashboard-line text-pink-500"></i> Dashboard
        </a>
        <a href="/sessions" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-pink-50 transition-colors text-sm text-gray-700">
          <i class="ri-qr-code-line text-pink-500"></i> Sessions
        </a>
        <a href="/contacts" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-pink-50 transition-colors text-sm text-gray-700">
          <i class="ri-contacts-line text-pink-500"></i> Contacts
        </a>
        <a href="/developer" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-pink-50 transition-colors text-sm text-gray-700">
          <i class="ri-code-box-line text-pink-500"></i> API Docs
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
